          "text": "小弟两次去见曹操，无奈他高挂免见牌，不容我相见，是弟封金挂印，修书一"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "封，送往曹营，意欲不辞而别。特请二位皇嫂登车。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘夫人、糜夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若途中有人拦阻，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位皇嫂，但放宽心，只是小弟这青龙刀，管叫他难逃公道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘夫人、糜夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全凭二叔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众小校，趱行者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
