    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二门官",
        "关羽",
        "门官甲",
        "马童"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二门官同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了丞相令，把守许昌门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖风入松〗。关羽、二皇嫂、四马童同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开关！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人叫关？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关将军保定二位皇嫂过关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有丞相将令？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有丞相公文？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也无有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一无丞相将令，二无公文，要想出关，是万万不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等敢挡某家的去路么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人不敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谅尔也不敢。小校，催车！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "门官甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，你看他吹胡子瞪眼，实在可怕，我们快快报于丞相知道，便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二门官同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
