    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二门官",
        "小军",
        "张辽",
        "曹操",
        "程昱"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四将、郭嘉、程昱同上。大吹场。曹操上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爕理阴阳，统雄兵，坐镇许昌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有关将军书信一封，丞相请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呈上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。曹操看信。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦哈哈呀，关公封金挂印，竟是去心一定，真乃是义人也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二门官同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启丞相：今有关公，保定二位皇嫂，怒气不息，闯出城去。小人等拦挡不住，"
        },
        {
          "character": "二门官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "特来禀报丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你等无干，再探。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二门官同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，不料此人，竟自去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看关公志高气扬，情性狂妄，不辞丞相，竟敢修书前来，真乃胆大妄为。丞相"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何不将他赶回杀之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人英雄出众，仗义轻财，不忘故主，吾甚敬之爱之。张辽听令，命你速速赶"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去，见了关公，叫他少待一时，老夫还要亲自送他一程，以表旧日之情，快去"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位将军，随同老夫前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，与爷带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "适才间众军校报连番，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "许昌城走了关美髯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见了关公说根源。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
