    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "不远千里把兄找",
        "人来与爷前引道",
        "众人",
        "关羽",
        "千两黄金他不要",
        "在许昌我与他相交好",
        "官封我汉寿亭侯皇恩浩荡",
        "张辽",
        "我念他英雄盖世武艺好",
        "曹操",
        "望丞相开恩将某放",
        "白马坡前无能将",
        "自从下邳来归降",
        "都只为刘备投了贼袁绍",
        "非是我关某太狂妄"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四马童、甘夫人、糜夫人、关羽同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "挂印信封黄金来去清白，冠冕堂皇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "暗用那牢笼计打动我关云长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我看他到如今枉费心肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "青龙刀、赤兔马保定皇娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见一人骑战马急走慌忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张辽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关将军请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是文远贤弟，你此番前来，莫非丞相，叫关某回转么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非也。丞相言道：请将军少待片时，丞相要亲自送将军一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纵然丞相，就是带来铁甲雄兵，关某也要决一死战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "张辽把话对我讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到叫关某无主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（甘夫人、糜夫人同下，关羽、马童同上桥。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "等候曹军作商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操 （内西皮导板） 人马纷纷出城壕，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、三将、郭嘉、程昱引曹操同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不料关公竟脱逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "义气凌云盖九霄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "赠他的上马金、下马银，美女战马和锦袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他不忘桃园故旧交。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可算得世间一英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见一人立马在长桥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我念他英雄盖世武艺好"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在许昌我与他相交好"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "都只为刘备投了贼袁绍"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不远千里把兄找"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人来与爷前引道"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关将军你为何去心太急？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相容禀：某本解良一武夫，自幼投侍刘皇叔，桃园结义，誓同生死，皇天厚"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "土，共鉴此衷。前在下邳，曾请三事，均蒙丞相恩准。昨日闻得故主刘玄德，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在河北袁绍军中，是某一闻此言，寸心如割，追念前盟，恨不得插翅飞去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是：大丈夫义不负心，忠不顾死，新恩虽厚，旧义难忘，倘有未尽之恩，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "容俟异日图报。昨日挂金封印，缴还丞相，还望丞相无忘昔日之言，为幸也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "勒马提刀把话讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊一声丞相听端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蒙丞相带我见君王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蒙丞相赐我锦袍、战马、美女、琼浆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "某也曾诛文丑，斩却颜良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "桃园恩情时时挂在心肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "知恩报德不敢忘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自从下邳来归降"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "官封我汉寿亭侯皇恩浩荡"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "白马坡前无能将"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是我关某太狂妄"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "望丞相开恩将某放"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听罢言来心欢畅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忠义英雄世无双。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自从下邳来归降"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "官封我汉寿亭侯皇恩浩荡"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "白马坡前无能将"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是我关某太狂妄"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "望丞相开恩将某放"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫欲与将军朝夕相随，共扶汉室，不料将军去心已定，老夫也不敢强留，现"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备黄金千两，与将军作路途之费。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将黄金献上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久承丞相厚恩，感激不尽。某尚有川资，就将黄金分赏丞相之将士可也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军真妙人也，既不收此黄金，现有锦袍一袭，聊以作别，望将军收纳乎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人言将军义气高，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "仗义轻财大英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只得献上锦战袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "千两黄金他不要"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "丞相待我恩谊好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "临别又赠我锦战袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "千两黄金他不要"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹营中将士杀气高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又有那许褚和张辽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮紧板",
          "musical_style": "西皮紧板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恐怕中了计笼牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽挑袍，下桥。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "催马加鞭下长桥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹丞相，赠我战袍，足见多情。今日一别，后会有期。异日相逢，定当厚报，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关某去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见关公他去了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好叫老夫心内焦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关公已去，老夫少却一员战将，真真可惜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，带马回营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
